### SentinelAI — Manual test payloads
### Use with VS Code REST Client extension or httpie
### Proxy must be running on localhost:8080

### 1. Baseline clean request
GET http://localhost:8080/get
User-Agent: Mozilla/5.0

###

### 2. SQL Injection (A03)
GET http://localhost:8080/get?id=1'+UNION+SELECT+username,password+FROM+users--
User-Agent: Mozilla/5.0

###

### 3. XSS (A03)
POST http://localhost:8080/post
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "comment": "<script>alert('xss')</script>",
  "user": "attacker"
}

###

### 4. SSRF — cloud metadata (A10)
GET http://localhost:8080/get?url=http://169.254.169.254/latest/meta-data/
User-Agent: Mozilla/5.0

###

### 5. JWT alg:none (A07) — header: eyJhbGciOiJub25lIiwidHlwIjoiSldUIn0
GET http://localhost:8080/get
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJub25lIiwidHlwIjoiSldUIn0.eyJzdWIiOiJhZG1pbiJ9.

###

### 6. Token in URL (A07)
GET http://localhost:8080/get?api_key=supersecrettoken12345678

###

### 7. Sensitive data in request body (A02)
POST http://localhost:8080/post
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "MyP@ssw0rd123"
}

###

### 8. Admin path without auth (A01)
GET http://localhost:8080/admin/users

###

### 9. Mass assignment / privilege escalation (A08)
POST http://localhost:8080/post
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "alice",
  "is_admin": true,
  "role": "admin"
}

###

### 10. Known scanner User-Agent (A09)
GET http://localhost:8080/get
User-Agent: sqlmap/1.7.8

###
